{"tid":649934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍候任太平洋司令：若想阻止中國控制南海　惟有訴諸武力","createTime":"2018-05-02T02:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T02:37:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"452dacc87f368b50d6a86450ca499aa3000fa894","tid":649934,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:07:38.000Z","msg":"美國《新聞周刊》上周五（20日）報道稱，美軍候任太平洋司令、四星上將戴維森（Philip Davidson）向美國參議院軍事委員會提交一份書面報告，大肆渲染中國軍事威脅論，並指出要想阻止中國控制南海，惟有進行「武裝衝突」這一條路。<br />\n<br />\n戴維森上周五（20日）表示：「中國在亞太地區不停擴大軍事部署，修建秘密軍事基地。中國解放軍已經有徹底掌控該地區的能力，南海其他國家無法與之爭奪。」<br />\n<br />\n他續指，一旦中國完全佔領南海，北京就可以將其影響力深入到澳洲。而中國解放軍可以以此為據點，挑戰美國在該區域的軍事存在，並碾壓其他國家的軍力。戴維森甚至鼓動美國向中國「開戰」，認為美國若要阻止中國控制南海，只有訴諸武力。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，此前有軍事專家指出美軍類似的報告層出不窮，目的是向美國國會「要錢」。由於讓國會為軍隊撥款並非易事，所以極力營造「中國威脅論」的氛圍成了他們的一大「捷徑」。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部部長王毅3月曾指出，南海面臨最主要的挑戰就是一些外部勢力對南海風平浪靜心有不安，總想挑動是非，唯恐天下不亂。說到軍事化，動輒把全副武裝的艦船、飛機，開到南海來炫耀武力，這才是影響南海和平穩定的最大干擾因素。<br />\n<br />\n現年61歲的美軍太平洋司令哈里斯（Harry Harris）5月退休，並將轉到澳洲擔任美國駐當地大使，因此總統特朗普（Donald Trump）決定任命現任海軍艦隊司令部司令戴維森接任他的職務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/181164/%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4-%E8%8B%A5%E6%83%B3%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7-%E6%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%B4%E8%AB%B8%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2591%2598%2F181164%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%2580%2599%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7-%25E6%2583%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25AB%25B8%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%258A%259B&d=U%2FmuvXwI1vujrWW5Gmd3hNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5093551c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E6%96%87%E6%91%98/181164/%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%80%99%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E5%8F%B8%E4%BB%A4-%E8%8B%A5%E6%83%B3%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7-%E6%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E8%A8%B4%E8%AB%B8%E6%AD%A6%E5%8A%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2122ac5696724b9718af735a259a319951feb729","tid":649934,"uid":134215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"美帝海軍: 國會速速磅水 我要買新玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca839d30799d2b203f2cdce77da1ade60f928881","tid":649934,"uid":179467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2122ac5696724b9718af735a259a319951feb729","tid":649934,"uid":134215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"美帝海軍: 國會速速磅水 我要買新玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"應該係想要一隻福特級航母代替列根號 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2967566eb035d05c24165336284a7fd3e2ce2207","tid":649934,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.fei123.com/upload/2017/06/22/48f98a879517ce13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fei123.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F48f98a879517ce13.jpg&h=81a4275e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c4633fbb1845a0e9b591090e1e914cc457f0e1b","tid":649934,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2967566eb035d05c24165336284a7fd3e2ce2207","tid":649934,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.fei123.com/upload/2017/06/22/48f98a879517ce13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fei123.com%2Fupload%2F201